suffer from osteoporosis nowadays.

837
00:45:50,820 --> 00:45:51,540
Doctor.

838
00:45:51,730 --> 00:45:53,090
A playboy like him

839
00:45:53,090 --> 00:45:54,570
doesn't play video games.

840
00:45:54,570 --> 00:45:56,090
They're too busy socializing.

841
00:45:57,130 --> 00:45:59,210
Look at his face. Pale as a ghost.

842
00:45:59,730 --> 00:46:02,090
It's proof of his corrupt life.

843
00:46:05,170 --> 00:46:06,090
Quite so.

844
00:46:07,500 --> 00:46:09,770
Fortunately, you only suffered
a minor dislocation this time.

845
00:46:10,860 --> 00:46:12,060
I'll set it back in place.

846
00:46:12,250 --> 00:46:13,860
You can come back
and remove the sling in a few days.

847
00:46:14,290 --> 00:46:15,980
But bear in mind.

